title: Gamers converge on New Orleans for MLG World Finals
text: Gamers converge on New Orleans for MLG World Finals By Associated Press | October 17, 2015 @ 7:48 am \n Vendor Mike Gaboury kisses Darshelle Stevens as they work the booth of Filthy Casual, a clothing line, at the the Major League Gaming World Finals in New Orleans, Friday, Oct. 16, 2015. Thousands of people are converging on New Orleans this weekend for the tournament. Players from around the world are competing in such games as Call of Duty: Advanced Warfare and Dota 2. The event started Friday and goes through Sunday at the convention center. (AP Photo/Gerald Herbert)\n
